---
title: Popcorn Chicken Dinner with Mashed Potatoes and Salad
description: Everyone is going to love this fun and easy family dinner! The combo of juicy Southern style popcorn chicken with a BBQ sauce dipper, creamy mash and fresh greens is going to make sure there is nothing but clean plates tonight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-popcorn-95e1a7b3.jpg
